text: Nolan Ray Rogers (July 3, 1931 - December 18, 2020) was an American Republican politician and businessman. He was born in Pearl, Mississippi. Rogers was a member of the Mississippi House of Representatives from 1984 until 2020. Rogers died on December 18, 2020 at the age of 89. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2020 deaths Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from Mississippi Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Businesspeople from Mississippi
